      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable sedan in good condition, well-suited for a driver seeking a reliable and well-maintained vehicle. The exterior remains in great shape, showing only minor cosmetic signs of use like small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all features functioning as they should. It has a solid service history and drives smoothly, offering a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
