    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in pristine condition. It drives like a total dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically perfect, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
