      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with its high-pressure Double-VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies. This example retains its factory-spec subframe integrity and features a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission. The limited-slip M Differential Lock operates flawlessly, delivering power to the rear wheels with surgical precision. Meticulously maintained with a documented valve adjustment history and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle offers a pure, visceral driving experience free of mechanical compromise.",
      "price": 46500.0,
